sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_script_include"><sys_script_include action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><access>public</access><active>true</active><api_name>x_pisn_sp_launchp.SpLaunchpadAPI</api_name><caller_access/><client_callable>false</client_callable><description/><name>SpLaunchpadAPI</name><script><![CDATA[var SpLaunchpadAPI = Class.create();
SpLaunchpadAPI.prototype = {
	initialize: function() {
	},

	getData: function(table, filter, limit, attributes) {
		var records = [];
		var gr = new GlideRecord(table);
		gr.addEncodedQuery(filter);
		if(limit)
			gr.setLimit(limit);
		else
			gr.setLimit(3);

		var attrs = '';
		if(attributes){
			attributes.split(',').forEach(function(element) {
				attrs = attrs + element.trim() + ',';
			});
		}
		else
			attrs = 'number,short_description,state,opened_by,assigned_to,sys_updated_on';

		gr.query();
		var record = {};
		while(gr.next()){
			record = {};
			record.v = {};
			record.dv = {};
			$sp.getRecordValues(record.v,gr,attrs);
			$sp.getRecordDisplayValues(record.dv,gr,attrs);

			var updated_on_gdt = new GlideDateTime(gr.getValue('sys_updated_on'));
			record.date_updated_on = updated_on_gdt.getLocalDate().getDisplayValue() + ' ' + updated_on_gdt.getLocalTime().getDisplayValue();
            record.sys_id = gr.getUniqueValue();
			record.table = gr.getTableName();

			records.push(record);
		}

		return {
			records: records,
			fields: this.__getFields(attrs,gr),
			table: table,
			filter: filter,
			count: this.getCount(table,filter),
			limit: limit
		};
	},

	__getFields: function(attributes,gr){
		var attrs = [];
		var attrsArray = attributes.split(',');
		for(var i in attrsArray){ if(attrsArray[i]!="sys_id")
				attrs.push({
					name: attrsArray[i],
					field: $sp.getField(gr,attrsArray[i])
				});
		}
		return attrs;
	},

	getCount: function(table,filter){
		var grAggr = new GlideAggregate(table);
		grAggr.addEncodedQuery(filter);
		grAggr.addAggregate('COUNT');
		grAggr.query();
		var count = 0;
		while (grAggr.next()) {
			count = grAggr.getAggregate('COUNT');
		}
		return count;
	},

		type: 'SpLaunchpadAPI'
	};]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script_include</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>fabio</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2019-05-20 11:00:50</sys_created_on><sys_id>aca10299db25f700efd54a92ba961934</sys_id><sys_mod_count>47</sys_mod_count><sys_name>SpLaunchpadAPI</sys_name><sys_package display_value="SP Launchpad" source="x_pisn_sp_launchp">f400c295db25f700efd54a92ba961934</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="SP Launchpad">f400c295db25f700efd54a92ba961934</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_include_aca10299db25f700efd54a92ba961934</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>fabio</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2019-05-23 13:05:55</sys_updated_on></sys_script_include></record_update>
